import React, { Fragment } from 'react' import { Link, useNavigate} from "react-router-dom"; import CheckoutSteps from './CheckoutSteps' import { useSelector } from 'react-redux' const ConfirmOrder = () => { const history = useNavigate(); const { callCardItems, loanInfo } = useSelector(state => state.cart) const userLogin = useSelector(state => state.userLogin); const { userInfo } = userLogin; // Calculate Order Prices const itemsPrice = callCardItems.reduce((acc, item) => acc + item.unitPrice * item.quantity, 0) const shippingPrice = itemsPrice > 200 ? 0 : 25 const totalPrice = (itemsPrice + shippingPrice).toFixed(2) const processToPayment = () => { const data = { itemsPrice: itemsPrice.toFixed(2), shippingPrice, totalPrice, } sessionStorage.setItem('orderInfo', JSON.stringify(data)) history('/success'); } return (

Loan Info

Name: {userInfo && userInfo.username}

Phone: {loanInfo.phoneNo}

Address: {`${loanInfo.address}, ${loanInfo.city}, ${loanInfo.country}`}

Your Cart Items:

{callCardItems.map(item => (
{item.book_name}

{item.quantity} x {item.unitPrice.toLocaleString('it-IT', { style: 'currency', currency: 'VND' })} = {(item.quantity * item.unitPrice.toLocaleString('it-IT', { style: 'currency', currency: 'VND' })).toFixed(2)}

 ))}

Order Summary

Subtotal: ${itemsPrice}

Shipping: ${shippingPrice}

Total: ${totalPrice}

 ) } export default ConfirmOrder
